<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.3">
<l>kattak katittuk kiṭanta peruñcelva</l>
<l>mottup poruntikkoṇ ṭuṇṇātu maṇṇāḷvāṉ</l>
<l>kottut talaivaṉ kuṭikeṭat tōṉṟiya</l>
<l>vattaṉvan teṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">āyarka ḷēṟeṉ puṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[He] who appeared in order to ruin</l>
<l>the clan of the leader of the assembly,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who ruled the land,</l>
<l rend="indent">having not himself agreed to concede the great wealth</l>
<l rend="indent">that had accumulated,</l>
<l>comes, the Lord will embrace me [from] behind.</l>
<l>The bull of the cowherds will me [from] behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
